flowRoot.flowPara: openSUSE 11.4 is a powerful and free Linux-based operating system for your computer. Surf the web, work on your documents while listening to music, set up a server or develop software. The choice is yours and you'll have a lot of fun! The openSUSE Project, a worldwide community that promotes the use of Linux everywhere, creates this Linux distribution in a open and transparent way as part of the global Free and Open Source Software movement. Learn more about openSUSE and become a part of it at

System Requirements: This operating system will run on most modern PCs with at least 512MB of RAM and 4GB of disk space
This DVD includes everything you need to get your desktop, laptop, or server up and running with Linux.
You can also take 11.4 for a test drive before you install it - just boot your computer from this DVD.
